sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import Modal from 'react-bootstrap/Modal'; import {Button} from 'react-bootstrap'; import Title from '../components/Common/Title/Title' export default function FinalPayment(props) { return ( </Modal.Title> </Modal.Header> <Modal.Body> <div className="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 pt-5 pb-0 pl-0 pr-0"> <div className="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-6 pt-5 pb-0 pl-0 pr-0"> <span>Amount:</span><span>500Rs</span> </div> <div className="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-6 pt-5 pb-0 pl-0 pr-0"> <span>Type:</span><span>One - time Donation</span> </div> </div> <div className="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 pt-5 pb-0 pl-0 pr-0"> <span>Enter your UPI ID : </span> </div> </Modal.Body> <Modal.Footer> <Button onClick={props.onHide} className="modalCancel">Cancel</Button> <Button className="modalProceed">Proceed</Button> </Modal.Footer> </Modal> ); }
